# Style Rewrite Tab — Code Review & Pipeline Walkthrough

## Architecture Overview

The Style Rewrite tab has **2 modes** that share the same UI but run **completely different backend pipelines**:

| | **Top/List Review** | **Narrative** |
|---|---|---|
| Pipeline function | [_do_renew_review()](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/ui/rewrite_style_tab.py#2605-3524) | [_do_renew_style()](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/ui/rewrite_style_tab.py#2056-2559) |
| Steps | **12 steps** | **8 steps** |
| Style filter | `pipeline: "review"` styles | `pipeline: "narrative"` styles |
| Blueprint extractor | [extract_blueprint_review()](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/core/rewriter.py#1047-1091) | [extract_blueprint()](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/core/rewriter.py#1004-1045) |
| Outline creator | [create_review_outline()](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/core/rewriter.py#2283-2415) / [create_mystery_outline()](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/core/rewriter.py#2146-2281) | [generate_renew_outline_v2()](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/core/rewriter.py#1194-1252) |
| Writer | [write_review_chapter()](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/core/rewriter.py#2417-2599) | [write_from_blueprint()](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/core/rewriter.py#1322-1404) |
| Cross-chapter review | [review_cross_chapter()](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/core/rewriter.py#1148-1192) | [review_narrative_full()](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/core/rewriter.py#1489-1533) |
| Extra features | Price Check, Reality Check, Unit Conversion, Unused Chapters | — |

---

## Entry Point & Job Dispatch

```mermaid
flowchart TB
    A["▶ Rewrite button clicked"] --> B["_do_rewrite()"]
    B --> C{"Multiple folders?"}
    C -->|Yes| D{"User choice"}
    D -->|"⚡ Riêng"| E["_do_rewrite_each()"]
    D -->|"🔗 Gộp"| F["_do_rewrite_merge()"]
    C -->|No| E
    
    B --> N["Niche Check\n(AI Flash detect)"]
    N -->|Mismatch| N2{"User confirms?"}
    N2 -->|Run all| E
    N2 -->|Matched only| E
    N2 -->|Cancel| STOP

    E --> G["_create_and_submit_job()\nper folder"]
    F --> G2["_create_and_submit_job()\nmerged"]

    G --> H{"Mode?"}
    G2 --> H
    H -->|"Top/List Review"| I["_do_renew_review()"]
    H -->|"Narrative"| J["_do_renew_style()"]
    
    I --> K{"Cut Video ON?"}
    J --> K
    K -->|Yes| L["_do_cut_video_for_group()"]
    K -->|No| M["✅ Done"]
    L --> M
```

**Key mechanisms:**
- Jobs run in a `ThreadPoolExecutor(max_workers=3)`
- Each job has its own `stop_event` (threading.Event) for cancellation
- [_stopped()](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/ui/rewrite_style_tab.py#2652-2656) callback propagated to every `APIClient` for immediate abort
- UI updates via `pyqtSignal`: [progress_text](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/ui/rewrite_style_tab.py#995-1010), `tree_refresh`, `job_update`

