## Top/List Review Pipeline (12 Steps)

> Function: [_do_renew_review()](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/ui/rewrite_style_tab.py#L2605)

```mermaid
flowchart TB
    S1["1️⃣ Concatenate\nall input .txt"] --> S2["2️⃣ Detect Framework\n(detect_framework)"]
    S2 --> S3["3️⃣ Extract Blueprint\n(extract_blueprint_review)"]
    S3 --> S4["4️⃣ Recommend Framework\n(recommend_framework → popup)"]
    S4 --> S5["5️⃣ Reality Check\n(reality_check_blueprint)"]
    S5 --> S5b["5b Price Enrichment\n(enrich_prices_google)"]
    S5b --> S6["6️⃣ Check Completeness\n(check_blueprint)"]
    S6 --> S7["7️⃣ Convert Units\n(convert_units)"]
    S7 --> S8["8️⃣ Create Outline\n(create_review_outline)"]
    S8 --> S9["9️⃣ Audit Outline\n(audit_outline_review)"]
    S9 --> S10["🔟 Write Chapters\n(write_review_chapter) × N"]
    S10 --> S11["1️⃣1️⃣ Cross-Chapter Review\n+ Auto Patch"]
    S11 --> S12["1️⃣2️⃣ Merge\n→ FULL_SCRIPT.txt\n+ Unused chapters copy"]
```

### Step Details

| Step | What | AI Function | Prompt | Output File |
|------|------|-------------|--------|-------------|
| 1 | Concat all input text | — | — | (in-memory) |
| 2 | Detect original framework | [detect_framework()](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/core/rewriter.py#930-1002) | [system_detect_framework.txt](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/prompts/system_detect_framework.txt) | `_pipeline/_detection.json` |
| 3 | Extract blueprint (products, specs, pros/cons) | [extract_blueprint_review()](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/core/rewriter.py#1047-1091) | [system_extract_blueprint_review.txt](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/prompts/system_extract_blueprint_review.txt) | `_pipeline/_blueprint_raw.json` |
| 4 | AI ranks frameworks → user popup | [recommend_framework()](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/core/rewriter.py#1631-1686) | [system_recommend_framework.txt](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/prompts/system_recommend_framework.txt) | `_pipeline/_rankings.json` |
| 5 | Verify facts, fix errors, enrich data | [reality_check_blueprint()](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/core/rewriter.py#1882-1932) | [system_reality_check.txt](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/prompts/system_reality_check.txt) | `_pipeline/_reality_check.json` + `_blueprint.json` |
| 5b | Google Search price lookup (firearms niche) | [enrich_prices_google()](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/core/rewriter.py#1934-2090) | Gemini + Google Search grounding | `_pipeline/_price_enrichment.json` |
| 6 | Check data completeness vs framework needs | [check_blueprint()](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/core/rewriter.py#1688-1743) | [system_check_blueprint.txt](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/prompts/system_check_blueprint.txt) | `_pipeline/_completeness_check.json` |
| 7 | Convert units (metric/imperial by country) | [convert_units()](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/core/rewriter.py#1745-1880) | — (rule-based) | `_pipeline/_blueprint_converted.json` |
| 8 | Create chapter outline | [create_review_outline()](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/core/rewriter.py#2283-2415) or [create_mystery_outline()](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/core/rewriter.py#2146-2281) | [system_review_outline.txt](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/prompts/system_review_outline.txt) | `_pipeline/_review_outline.json` |
| 9 | Audit outline structure | [audit_outline_review()](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/core/rewriter.py#1093-1146) | [system_audit_outline_review.txt](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/prompts/system_audit_outline_review.txt) | `_pipeline/_audit.json` + `_review_outline_audited.json` |
| 10 | Write each chapter sequentially | [write_review_chapter()](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/core/rewriter.py#2417-2599) | [system_write_from_blueprint_review.txt](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/prompts/system_write_from_blueprint_review.txt) | `ch_01_Intro.txt`, `ch_02_ProductName.txt`, ... |
| 11 | Cross-chapter review + auto-patch | [review_cross_chapter()](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/core/rewriter.py#1148-1192) + [patch_chapter_overlap()](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/core/rewriter.py#1535-1585) | [system_review_cross_chapter.txt](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/prompts/system_review_cross_chapter.txt) | `_pipeline/_review.json` |
| 12 | Merge + copy unused | — | — | `FULL_SCRIPT.txt` + `_pipeline/_source_mapping.json` |

### Review Pipeline Special Features

**Product Shuffling (Step 8):** Before creating the outline, products are shuffled randomly and ordering clues (`comparisons`, `narrative_moments`, `source_parts`) are stripped. This prevents the AI from simply replicating the source order.

**Unused Chapters (Step 12):** Products not selected by the outline are tracked. Their source chapter files are copied to the "Unused" folder for potential reuse.

**Price Check (Step 5b):** Only activates when:
1. `💰 Price Check` checkbox is ON
2. Style niche matches firearms/ammo keywords
3. Gemini API keys are configured in header bar

**Transitions Toggle:** When `↔ Transitions` is OFF, transition-related issues in the cross-chapter review are filtered out.

